FBIS3-36448 "drsov025_b_94012" FBIS-SOV-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Feb 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Golushko Announces Arrest of Antistate Spy LD0402113094 Moscow Radio Moscow in Russian to Tajikistan 1700 GMT 3 Feb 94 LD0402113094 Moscow Radio Moscow Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Radio Slavyanka" program of the Russian Defense Ministry] [Text] General Nikolay Golushko, director of the Federal Counterintelligence Service, has announced that in January a Russian citizen, whose activity had caused serious damage to the state, was arrested. According to prelimiary assessments, the damage caused to the state is on a par with that caused by [Oleg] Penkovskiy.
